<item>
            <title>[TIKA-3109] Ingest attachment: failed to extract text from iframe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-3109</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This standalone &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/files/4757855/c0711285-8ab7-46c3-b730-7c0639466537.html.zip&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;HTML&lt;/a&gt; page has all its CSS/JS/IMAGEs embedded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; After indexing it using ElasticSearch, we tried to search the keyword &lt;b&gt;logarithmic&lt;/b&gt; which exists. Unfortunately, we couldn&apos;t find it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dadoonet&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dadoonet&quot;&gt;dadoonet&lt;/a&gt; was able to reproduce the issue which is fully described &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/issues/57924&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;elasticsearch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Apache Tika 1.22&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Java&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;java 13.0.2 2020-01-14&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Ubuntu 18.04.1 LTS&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;Linux XXXXX 4.15.0-101-generic #102-Ubuntu SMP Mon May 11 10:07:26 UTC 2020 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</environment>
